<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA96">
<l>attiyū rāṉpuḷḷai yūrvā ṉaṇimaṇiyiṉ</l>
<l>ṟutticcēr nākattiṉ mēṟṟuyilvāṉ – mūttī</l>
<l>maṟaiyāvāṉ mākaṭaṉañ cuṇṭāṉ ṟaṉakku</l>
<l>miṟaiyāvā ṉeṅkaḷ pirāṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one whose village is Atti, who mounts the bird, who sleeps on the snake</l>
<l>with hood spots like decorative gems, who is the Veda</l>
<l>of the three fires, who is the lord of the one who ate the poison</l>
<l>from the big ocean, [he is] our Lord.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
